"floors, mills, and bakeries to keep your workers fed."
msgstr ""
"Brood is een basisvoedingsmiddel voor de Hebreeuwse economie. Bouw "
"boerderijen, dorsvloeren, molens en bakkerijen om je arbeiders te voeden."

#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/tips.lua:12
msgid ""
"The Hebrew tribe uses copper instead of iron. Ensure a steady supply of "
"copper ore from your mines."
msgstr ""
"De Hebreeuwse stam gebruikt koper in plaats van ijzer. Zorg voor een "
"constante aanvoer van kopererts uit je mijnen."

#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/tips.lua:16
msgid ""
"Cloth is essential for Hebrew construction. Set up a wool production chain: "
"shepherds, spinning mills, and weaving mills."
msgstr ""
"Doek is essentieel voor de Hebreeuwse bouw. Zet een wolproductieketen op: "
"herders, spinnerijen en weverijen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Branch, part 1
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:100
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"Branches are collected from the ground near trees by the branch collector."
msgstr ""
"Takken worden door de takkenverzamelaar van de grond bij bomen verzameld."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Branch, part 2
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:102
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"They are the primary building material alongside clay and granite, and are "
"also used as fuel for smelting copper."
msgstr ""
"Ze zijn naast klei en graniet het belangrijkste bouwmateriaal en worden ook "
"gebruikt als brandstof voor het smelten van koper."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Log
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:112
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"Logs are a vital building material for the Hebrews. They can obtain wood by "
"clearing trees at a clearing tent or by trading menorahs at Solomon's "
"Harbour."
msgstr ""
"Houtblokken zijn een essentieel bouwmateriaal voor de Hebreeën. Ze kunnen "
"hout verkrijgen door bomen te kappen in een open plek of door menorahs te "
"verhandelen in Solomon's Harbour."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Granite, part 1
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:122
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Granite is a basic building material."
msgstr "Graniet is een fundamenteel bouwmateriaal."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Granite, part 2
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:124
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"The Hebrews' stonemasons cut granite blocks in quarries and granite mines."
msgstr ""
"De steenhouwers van de Hebreeën hakten granieten blokken in steengroeven en "
"granietmijnen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Clay, part 1
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:135
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Clay is a basic building material."
msgstr "Klei is een basisbouwmateriaal."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Clay, part 2
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:137
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid "The Hebrews produce clay by digging it from the earth in the clay pit."
msgstr "De Hebreeën produceren klei door deze uit de kleigroeve te graven."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Water, part 1
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:150
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Water is the essence of life!"
msgstr "Water is de essentie van het leven!"

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Water, part 2
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:152
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"Water is drawn from wells. It is used in the bakery, the winery and for clay "
"production."
msgstr ""
"Water wordt uit putten gehaald. Het wordt gebruikt in de bakkerij, de "
"wijnmakerij en voor de kleiproductie."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Wheat, part 1
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:162
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Wheat is essential for survival."
msgstr "Tarwe is essentieel om te overleven."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Wheat, part 2
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:164
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"Wheat is produced by farms. It is threshed into grains on the threshing "
"floor and then milled into flour for baking bread."
msgstr ""
"Tarwe wordt geproduceerd door boerderijen. Het wordt op de dorsvloer tot "
"graankorrels gedorst en vervolgens tot meel gemalen om brood te bakken."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Wheat Grains, part 1
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:174
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid "Wheat grains are threshed from harvested wheat on the threshing floor."
msgstr "Tarwekorrels worden gedorst van geoogste tarwe op de dorsvloer."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Wheat Grains, part 2
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:176
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid "They are ground into flour in the mill."
msgstr "Ze worden in de molen tot meel vermalen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Flour
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:186
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"Flour is ground from wheat grains in the mill and used in the bakery to bake "
"bread."
msgstr ""
"Meel wordt gemalen uit tarwekorrels in de molen en gebruikt in de bakkerij "
"om brood te bakken."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Bread
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:195
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"Bread is the main food for the Hebrews. It is baked from flour and water in "
"the bakery and used to feed miners and soldiers."
msgstr ""
"Brood is het belangrijkste voedsel voor de Hebreeën. Het wordt gebakken van "
"bloem en water in de bakkerij en gebruikt om mijnwerkers en soldaten te "
"voeden."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Fish
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:203
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid "Fish is caught by fishers and used to feed miners and soldiers."
msgstr ""
"Vis wordt gevangen door vissers en gebruikt om mijnwerkers en soldaten te "
"voeden."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Meat, part 1
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:212
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid "Meat is produced by the butchery from sheep."
msgstr "Vlees wordt geproduceerd door de slagerij van schapen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Meat, part 2
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:214
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid "It is used to feed miners and soldiers."
msgstr "Het wordt gebruikt om mijnwerkers en soldaten te voeden."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Olives
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:224
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"Olives are harvested in olive plantations and pressed into olive oil in the "
"mill."
msgstr ""
"Olijven worden geoogst in olijfboomgaarden en in de molen tot olijfolie "
"geperst."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Olive Oil
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:233
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"Olive oil is pressed from olives in the mill. It is used for food and in "
"religious ceremonies."
msgstr ""
"Olijfolie wordt in de molen uit olijven geperst. Het wordt gebruikt voor "
"voedsel en in religieuze ceremonies."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Grapes
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:242
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"Grapes are harvested in vineyards and used in the winery to produce wine."
msgstr ""
"Druiven worden geoogst in wijngaarden en gebruikt in de wijnmakerij om wijn "
"te produceren."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Wine
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:251
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"Wine is produced in the winery from grapes and water. It is used to feed "
"miners and soldiers."
msgstr ""
"Wijn wordt in de wijnmakerij geproduceerd uit druiven en water. Het wordt "
"gebruikt om mijnwerkers en soldaten te voeden."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Copper Ore, part 1
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:264
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Copper ore is mined in copper mines."
msgstr "Kopererts wordt gewonnen in kopermijnen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Copper Ore, part 2
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:266
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"It is smelted into copper in the clay furnace and used in the weapon smithy "
"to forge daggers."
msgstr ""
"Het wordt in de kleioven tot koper gesmolten en gebruikt in de wapensmidse "
"om dolken te smeden."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Copper, part 1
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:277
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid "Copper is smelted from copper ore in the clay furnace."
msgstr "Koper wordt gesmolten uit kopererts in een kleioven."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Copper, part 2
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:279
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid "It is used in the weapon smithy to forge daggers."
msgstr "Het wordt gebruikt in de wapensmidse om dolken te smeden."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Gold Ore, part 1
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:290
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Gold ore is mined in a gold mine."
msgstr "Gouderts wordt gedolven in een goudmijn."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Gold Ore, part 2
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:292
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"It is refined into gold leaf and menorahs in the gold beater's workshop."
msgstr ""
"Het wordt in de werkplaats van de goudsmid verwerkt tot bladgoud en menorahs."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Gold Leaf
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:302
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"Gold leaf is beaten from gold ore in the gold beater's workshop. It is used "
"to produce tefilin and tallitot."
msgstr ""
"Bladgoud wordt geslagen uit gouderts in het atelier van de goudsmid. Het "
"wordt gebruikt voor de vervaardiging van tefillin en tallietot."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Menorah
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:311
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"The menorah is a sacred seven-branched candelabrum made from gold ore. It is "
"used to train soldiers in the training camp."
msgstr ""
"De menorah is een heilige zevenarmige kandelaar gemaakt van gouderts. Hij "
"wordt gebruikt om soldaten te trainen in het trainingskamp."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Sheep
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:323
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"Sheep are raised by shepherds. They are brought to the butchery to produce "
"wool, meat and fur."
msgstr ""
"Schapen worden gehouden door herders. Ze worden naar de slager gebracht om "
"wol, vlees en vacht te produceren."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Wool
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:332
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"Wool is produced as a byproduct of the butchery when processing sheep. It is "
"spun into yarn in the spinning mill."
msgstr ""
"Wol wordt geproduceerd als bijproduct van het slachten van schapen. Het "
"wordt in de spinnerij tot garen gesponnen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Fur
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:341
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"Fur is a byproduct of the butchery when processing sheep. It is used to "
"produce tefilin and slingshots."
msgstr ""
"Vacht is een bijproduct van het slachten van schapen. Het wordt gebruikt "
"voor de productie van tefillin en katapulten."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Yarn
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:350
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"Yarn is spun from wool in the spinning mill. It is used to weave cloth and "
"to produce zizit."
msgstr ""
"Garen wordt gesponnen uit wol in de spinnerij. Het wordt gebruikt om stoffen "
"te weven en om zizit te produceren."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Cloth
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:359
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"Cloth is woven from yarn in the weaving mill. It is used to produce tallitot "
"and tunics in the dressmakery."
msgstr ""
"Stof wordt geweven van garen in de weverij. Het wordt gebruikt om tallitot "
"en tunieken te produceren in de kleermakerij."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Pick
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:371
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"Picks are used by stonemasons and miners. They are crafted in the workshop."
msgstr ""
"Hakhamers worden gebruikt door steenhouwers en mijnwerkers. Ze worden "
"vervaardigd in de werkplaats."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Hammer, part 1
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:381
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "The hammer is an essential tool."
msgstr "De hamer is een essentieel gereedschap."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Hammer, part 2
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:383
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"Geologists and builders all need a hammer. They are crafted in the workshop."
msgstr ""
"Geologen en bouwvakkers hebben allemaal een hamer nodig. Ze worden "
"vervaardigd in de werkplaats."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Fishing Rod, part 1
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:394
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Fishing rods are needed by fishers to catch fish."
msgstr "Vissers hebben hengels nodig om vis te vangen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Fishing Rod, part 2
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:396
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid "Fishing rods are crafted in the workshop."
msgstr "Hengels worden vervaardigd in de werkplaats."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Zizit
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:409
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"Zizit are ritual fringes made from yarn. They are attached to garments as "
"commanded by the Torah and used to train soldiers."
msgstr ""
"Zizit zijn rituele franjes gemaakt van garen. Ze worden aan kledingstukken "
"bevestigd zoals voorgeschreven door de Thora en worden gebruikt om soldaten "
"te trainen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Tallit Katan
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:418
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"A tallit katan is a ritual undergarment produced in the dressmakery. It "
"provides spiritual protection and is used to train soldiers."
msgstr ""
"Een tallit katan is een ritueel onderkleed dat in de kleermakerij wordt "
"vervaardigd. Het biedt spirituele bescherming en wordt gebruikt om soldaten "
"te trainen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Tefilin
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:427
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"Tefilin are small leather boxes containing Torah scrolls, crafted in the "
"Sofer's Workshop from wood, fur and gold leaf. They are used to train "
"soldiers."
msgstr ""
"Tefilin zijn kleine leren doosjes met Torah-rollen, vervaardigd in het "
"atelier van de Sofer uit hout, bont en bladgoud. Ze worden gebruikt om "
"soldaten te trainen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Tallit
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:436
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"The tallit is a prayer shawl produced in the dressmakery from cloth and gold "
"leaf. It provides the highest spiritual protection and is used to train "
"soldiers."
msgstr ""
"De talliet is een gebedsmantel die in de kleermakerij wordt vervaardigd uit "
"stof en bladgoud. Hij biedt de hoogste spirituele bescherming en wordt "
"gebruikt om soldaten te trainen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Tunic
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:448
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"A basic tunic is produced in the dressmakery from cloth. It is the initial "
"armor for Hebrew soldiers."
msgstr ""
"Een eenvoudige tuniek wordt in de kleermakerij gemaakt van stof. Het is het "
"eerste harnas voor Hebreeuwse soldaten."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Slingshot
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:457
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"The slingshot is a basic ranged weapon forged in the weapon smithy from fur "
"and granite. It is used to train soldiers in attack."
msgstr ""
"De katapult is een eenvoudig afstandswapen dat in de wapensmidse wordt "
"gemaakt van bont en graniet. Het wordt gebruikt om soldaten te trainen in "
"aanvallen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew ware: Dagger
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:466
msgctxt "hebrews_ware"
msgid ""
"A copper dagger is forged in the weapon smithy from copper and fur. It is "
"the strongest melee weapon of Hebrew soldiers."
msgstr ""
"Een koperen dolk wordt in de wapensmidse gesmeed uit koper en bont. Het is "
"het sterkste slagwapen van Hebreeuwse soldaten."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew worker: Carrier
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:482
msgctxt "hebrews_worker"
msgid "Carries items along your roads."
msgstr "Draagt voorwerpen langs je wegen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew worker: Ferry
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:489
msgctxt "hebrews_worker"
msgid "Ships wares across narrow rivers."
msgstr "Schepen hun waren over smalle rivieren."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew worker: Donkey
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:498
msgctxt "hebrews_worker"
msgid ""
"Donkeys help carry items along busy roads. They are raised on a donkey farm."
msgstr ""
"Ezels helpen bij het vervoeren van spullen langs drukke wegen. Ze worden "
"gefokt op een ezelboerderij."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew worker: Builder
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:508
msgctxt "hebrews_worker"
msgid "Works at construction sites to raise new buildings."
msgstr "Werkt op bouwwerven om nieuwe gebouwen op te trekken."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew worker: Stonemason
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:515
msgctxt "hebrews_worker"
msgid "Cuts raw pieces of granite out of rocks in the vicinity."
msgstr "Zaagt ruwe stukken graniet uit rotsen in de omgeving."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew worker: Branch Collector
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:522
msgctxt "hebrews_worker"
msgid ""
"Collects fallen branches from the ground near trees. The trees are not "
"harmed in the process."
msgstr ""
"Verzamelt afgevallen takken van de grond in de buurt van bomen. De bomen "
"worden daarbij niet beschadigd."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew worker: Miner
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:529
msgctxt "hebrews_worker"
msgid "Works deep in the mines to obtain copper ore, gold ore or granite."
msgstr "Werkt diep in de mijnen om kopererts, gouderts of graniet te winnen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew worker: Rebbe (displayed as geologist in-engine)
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:536
msgctxt "hebrews_worker"
msgid ""
"A Torah scholar and teacher. Rebbes discover resources for mining, lead the "
"Yeshiva, and educate the next generation of scholars."
msgstr ""
"Een Torah-geleerde en leraar. Rebbes ontdekken bronnen voor mijnbouw, leiden "
"de Yeshiva en leiden de volgende generatie geleerden op."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew worker: Scout
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:543
msgctxt "hebrews_worker"
msgid "Explores unknown territory."
msgstr "Verkent onbekend terrein."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew worker: Shipwright
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:550
msgctxt "hebrews_worker"
msgid "Works at the shipyard and constructs new ships."
msgstr "Werkt op de scheepswerf en bouwt nieuwe schepen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew worker: Fisher
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:560
msgctxt "hebrews_worker"
msgid "Catches fish in the nearby waters."
msgstr "Vist in de nabijgelegen wateren."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew worker: Farmer
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:567
msgctxt "hebrews_worker"
msgid "Plants and harvests wheat fields."
msgstr "Plant en oogst tarwevelden."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew worker: Shepherd
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:574
msgctxt "hebrews_worker"
msgid "Raises sheep and brings them to the butchery for processing."
msgstr "Fokt schapen en brengt ze naar de slagerij voor verwerking."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew worker: Talmid
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:586
msgctxt "hebrews_worker"
msgid ""
"A student who has begun Torah study. Talmidim work in specialized buildings "
"like the clay furnace. They are educated in the Yeshiva."
msgstr ""
"Een student die begonnen is met Torah-studie. Talmidim werken in "
"gespecialiseerde gebouwen zoals de kleioven. Ze worden opgeleid in de "
"Yeshiva."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew worker: Talmid Chacham
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:595
msgctxt "hebrews_worker"
msgid ""
"A wise student who has completed advanced studies. Talmidei Chachamim work "
"in the gold beater's workshop and other skilled positions. They are educated "
"in the Yeshiva."
msgstr ""
"Een wijze student die een hogere opleiding heeft afgerond. Talmidei "
"Chachamim werken in de goudsmederij en andere vakbekwame functies. Ze worden "
"opgeleid in de yeshiva."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew worker: Recruit
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:607
msgctxt "hebrews_worker"
msgid ""
"Recruits are produced at the Machane from Talmidim. They are then equipped "
"and initiated as soldiers at the Initiation Site."
msgstr ""
"Rekruten worden opgeleid in de Machane uit Talmidim. Vervolgens worden ze "
"uitgerust en ingewijd als soldaten op de Initiatielocatie."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Hebrew worker: Soldier
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:616
msgctxt "hebrews_worker"
msgid ""
"Soldiers defend your territory and conquer new land. Recruits are trained "
"into soldiers at the Initiation Site and gain experience in the training "
"camp."
msgstr ""
"Soldaten verdedigen je grondgebied en veroveren nieuw land. Rekruten worden "
"opgeleid tot soldaten op de Initiation Site en doen ervaring op in het "
"trainingskamp."

